    after zero-arg construction is all-False.
  - `test_ensure_default_primitives_fills_every_slot` — post-ensure
    snapshot is all-True; each slot's runtime type matches the
    canonical default (`ConnectionManager`, `LocalFileArtifactStore`,
    `ModelRegistry`, `FeatureStore`, `TrainingPipeline`,
    `ExperimentTracker`).
  - `test_ensure_default_primitives_is_idempotent` — identity
    preserved across two calls (zip-identity on the 6-tuple).
  - `test_di_injected_connection_manager_not_replaced` — injected
    `ConnectionManager` survives ensure; downstream registry +
